title.$value: Giellatekno/Divvun/UiT fst-based speller for Skolt Sami

info.description:
This is an fst-based speller for Skolt Sami. It is based
    on the normative subset of the morphological analyser for Skolt Sami.
    The source code can be found at:
    https://victorio.uit.no/langtech/trunk/langs/sms/
    License: GPL3+.

acceptor.description:
Giellatekno/Divvun/UiT dictionary for
    Skolt Sami compiled for HFST.

errmodel.description:
Correction model for keyboard misstrokes, at most 2 per
    word.
